title: fukumean

description.plain:
“fukumean” is a high-energy track where Gunna taps into the melodies that initially established him in the modern rap scene. Gunna specifically bounces back from a dark period of his life in good spirits, shown by confident, braggadocious lyrics.

As of 2023, it is Gunna’s best-performing song on the Billboard Hot 100 following “pushin P” which peaked at #7 on January 22, 2022.

Along with that accolade, it is his third top ten hit — reaching #4 during the charting week of August 5, 2023 — alongside “Lemonade” and aforementioned “pushin P.”
